    TvLite
    A stripped down object of the one returned via Ombi's /api/v1/Request/tvlite endpoint
    This class is, as far as I know, the only way to obtain the internal OMBI request ID number

    To get an array of this object, use OmbiCallers.getTvLiteArray()
